                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Tout train-train, rien qui dure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Oh ! À jamais",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Des créatures !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Cultes, Littératures,\nYeux chauds, lointains ou gais,\nInfinis au rabais,\nTout train-train, rien qui dure,\nOh ! À jamais\nDes créatures !"
        },
        {
